docs {
  Queue a task for execution. Supported task kinds:
  - install: Install a custom node
  - uninstall: Remove a custom node
  - update: Update a custom node
  - enable: Enable a disabled node
  - disable: Disable an enabled node

  Task params vary by kind. See process_task() in comfygit_server.py for details.
}
